\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0  Gil blinked. A second later he real Something clicked in his mind and he trotted over, dewflap flapping, ribs seeming to roll underneath his spine.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Poor old creature,\u8221\'94 Vigram muttered.}
