\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93That\u8217\'92s what it feels like when I use this tiny brush.\u8221\'94 Vigram held up a brush with thin, only a few horse-hairs wide. }
