\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Mandri said, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Uh\u8230\'85No, not anymore. I actually haven\u8217\'92t painted a picture in two years.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Really?\u8221\'94 Vigram interjected. \u8220\'93Then what have you been doing up on that little farm of yours.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Farming.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 It was common knowledge that Mandri\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s farm couldn\u8217\'92t grow a weed.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Ahhhhhh. Next time. Time for lunch.\u8221\'94 }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Then Vigram set his pallette down on the wicker end table that held, and he took, leaving Mandri to clean up.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Why don\u8217\'92t you paint anymore?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Well, the truth is, I just don\u8217\'92t think paintings are all that pretty.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Wouldn\u8217\'92t that be your fault?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Look, I just\u8230\'85\u8221\'94 Mandri tried to think of a more palatable excuse. \u8220\'93It\u8217\'92s expensive to paint. Look at this pigment. The canvas. Takes a man a week to . Your dad can afford it. I can\u8217\'92t.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Come work for my dad. You\u8217\'92d barely have to do more than scratch at paper.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 He\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92d stumbled into a trap.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Ehhhh\u8230\'85\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Don\u8217\'92t you think your dad\u8217\'92s business is a little\u8230\'85 exploitative?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Are you dense?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93No?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93My dad doesn\u8217\'92t actually care about learning to paint. The only reason he pays for the lessons is because you would die if he didn\u8217\'92t.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Is that how he feels about it?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I\u8217\'92ve seen your farm, that\u8217\'92s how it is.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I promise, you\u8217\'92ll love it here.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 She set her hands on her hips and said, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You\u8217\'92re not a eunuch, are you?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Excuse me, what?\u8221\'94}
